  "text": "An expert committee of child and adolescent obesity researchers was created in 1998 to make recommendations on prevention, assessment, and treatment of obesity based on clinical and scientific research [CITATION_1] . It was suggested that obesity treatment should focus on healthy eating and increasing physical activity of the child and family. This committee created guidelines to follow for successful treatment.",
